  "description": "There\u0026rsquo;s no way I\u0026rsquo;m linking to it but I just read a quote from someone saying \u0026ldquo;I\u0026rsquo;ll believe Long COVID is real when someone who isn\u0026rsquo;t bisexual has it\u0026rdquo; or something to that effect, after saying all the Zoomers that work for them are bisexual.\nAnd that\u0026rsquo;s just, a horrifying place for public health opinions to be, in every way. But also, the conflation of \u0026ldquo;bisexuals with long COVID\u0026rdquo; and \u0026ldquo;Zoomer\u0026rdquo; is good for my public image of being youthful, so there is that, I guess.\n",
